Spyglass licenses software to BMC . Spyglass Inc said Monday it licensed its embedded Web server software to BMC Software Inc for its PATROL CGI Server product . Terms of the agreement were not disclosed . BMC , a database management company will use the software to improve performance and security of Internet applications , Spyglass said . Spyglass provides software and services to make devices work with the World Wide Web . ( ( - - Chicago newsdesk , 312 - 408 - 8787 ) ) 
